{"tid":319520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"餐廳石油氣爆炸 林峰傷勢嚴重","createTime":"2017-07-13T00:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T12:17:52.000Z","uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b677c208e8b41ac50585853f4cc6ea3fd74a6f","tid":319520,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"本報訊】土瓜灣長寧街一間茶餐廳，昨清晨店員在廚房開石油爐炒餸期間突然爆炸，磚牆及假天花坍塌，巨大氣流捲起無數雜物飛出街外，波及4部車輛及對面店舖捲閘，店內4人受傷，其中一名食客慘被塌牆壓住，另一水吧工九成半皮膚燒傷，兩人皆性命垂危，機電署正調查爆炸原因。<br />\n記者：徐雲庭　周鴻熙　黎志偉<br />\n<br />\n4名傷者包括茶餐廳姓李（58歲）女東主、58歲水吧工人吳永光、53歲男食客林峰及63歲男食客黃英貴，其中吳傷勢最重，九成半皮膚燒傷，轉送威爾斯醫院治理，情況危殆；林則被塌下廚房磚牆壓住，頭、手及腳受傷，同樣情況危殆。而黃及女東主敷治後已出院。"},{"pid":"0c6f3f90b542b6d4e3fd9a9ddb9b25abe50556ee","tid":319520,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54535ecc66d87884c5be64b2fb79bf9434a1a7ad","tid":319520,"uid":12683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"無人理你咁慘 等我理下你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768e84ceccca216253322ee3691ff12a2db7e6ca","tid":319520,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947738b2d59d4ba4f29d3eae70c911c1b654d831","tid":319520,"uid":2312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"覆下你啦咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8307f5d04dae1aff6b471a327047f125aecaedb","tid":319520,"uid":5150